====================
Programs
====================
samples/gsm_test.py
Sends SMS text


samples/ir_test.py
Testing IR break beam.


samples/led.py
Testing writing to GPIO.


main.py
Temporary(?) main file.  	(Partially just to point out top functions)

*When cam.py is executed we need to forward that information to "gsm.py" to send 
a message "You're mail has been tampered with"


cam.py
Takes a picture,stores it on the SD card.


intrusion_check.py
Monitor the status of the door. 


door.py
Locks or unlock door. Before locking the door,"door.py" will check "door_open" status to
make sure the door is closed before locking.


mail_switch.py
Return "True" for mail present and "False" if there is not mail. Calls send_mail.py if true.


readmifare.py
Active only when door is locked. Reads card and unlocks door if correct card is used. No function
for incorrect card.


send_mail.py
Uses gsm module to send text "You have mail".


send_alert.py
Uses gsm module to send text "You mail has been broken into".



====================
GPIO Pins
====================
PN532:
CS = 18
MOSI = 23
MISO = 24
SCLK = 25

Lock:
OPEN/UNLOCK = 21
CLOSE/LOCK = 20

Door:
door_switch = 12

Mail:
Trigger = 36
YesMail = 32

Misc:
LED = 17
